{"tid":1648180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人權法或最快下周眾議院全體表決","createTime":"2019-10-12T05:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T05:54:18.000Z","uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"73e686fb322692cc004e0cf861075246b9bd8289","tid":1648180,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"人權法或最快下周眾議院全體表決<br />\n2019/10/12 13:31<br />\n《香港人權與民主法案》可能最快本港時間周三早上，在美國眾議院全體表決。<br />\n<br />\n根據眾議院最新日程，當地周二全體會議將處理八項法案，排第一的就是《香港人權與民主法案》，《保護香港法案》緊隨其後。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日會議的表決程序，最快本港時間周三上午六時半開始，法案可能會以「暫停適用議事規則」方式處理，這種做法屬於簡化程序，通常用於民主共和兩黨共識非常大的提案，不允許對提案內容進一步修改，討論限制在四十分鐘內，提案需要三分之二議員支持通過。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">14號希望見到大家坐爆港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ebf226982651e927b8a1e589edfe8243122a6e25","tid":1648180,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:37:49.000Z","msg":"source cable news tg"},{"pid":"5d0b68f2132a502db7e3b49dd2835605e414b73e","tid":1648180,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063ab5ab8315fc55ed83cbd60e6053d4ef3623a1","tid":1648180,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"［核彈行動］令警察家變！針對警妻開闢新文宣線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647500</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情請睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647500</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}